00:16:35.077 --> 00:16:36.537
(GROANING)

00:16:36.621 --> 00:16:38.414
(ALL LAUGHING)

00:16:40.958 --> 00:16:42.168
He's a complete wimp.

00:16:42.251 --> 00:16:45.796
What's it gonna be, McFly?
Are you in or out?

00:16:46.589 --> 00:16:48.549
I just... I'm not sure that I should.

00:16:48.633 --> 00:16:51.677
You know, because I think
that I should discuss it with my father.

00:16:51.761 --> 00:16:53.304
- Your father?
- Your father?

00:16:53.387 --> 00:16:55.598
Wrong answer, McFly! You lose!

00:16:55.681 --> 00:16:56.933
(SCREAMING)

00:16:58.851 --> 00:17:02.021
Okay, Griff, I'll do it. I'll do it, buddy.
Whatever you say.

00:17:02.104 --> 00:17:03.814
Stay down and shut up.

00:17:05.274 --> 00:17:06.901
Keep pedaling, you two!

00:17:17.954 --> 00:17:21.958
Now, let's hear the right answer.

00:17:23.459 --> 00:17:24.627
Well!

00:17:25.211 --> 00:17:28.130
Since when did you become
the physical type?

00:17:28.214 --> 00:17:29.924
The answer's no, Griff.

00:17:30.466 --> 00:17:32.718
- No?
- Yeah. What are you, deaf and stupid?

00:17:32.802 --> 00:17:34.470
I said no!

00:17:34.554 --> 00:17:36.806
What's wrong, McFly? Chicken?

00:17:39.642 --> 00:17:41.102
(SYNTHESIZED CLUCKING)

00:17:42.645 --> 00:17:44.981
What did you call me, Griff?

00:17:46.148 --> 00:17:48.317
Chicken, McFly!

00:17:48.401 --> 00:17:51.112
Nobody calls me

00:17:53.906 --> 00:17:55.324
chicken.

00:17:55.658 --> 00:17:57.034
(SCREAMING)

00:17:57.118 --> 00:17:58.411
- (ELECTRICITY SURGING)
- (GROANING)

00:17:59.829 --> 00:18:01.289
('80S POP MUSIC PLAYING)

00:18:02.373 --> 00:18:04.041
