Stop! Little girl, little girl. Stop.

00:18:27.857 --> 00:18:28.941
- Hey.
- Look,

00:18:29.025 --> 00:18:31.777
I need to borrow your Hoverboard.

00:18:32.278 --> 00:18:34.780
- Where is he?
- Here.

