It's called a DustBuster.

00:22:47.658 --> 00:22:50.244
- I can't lose.
- Marty! Marty! Up here!

00:22:50.327 --> 00:22:51.370
(WHISTLES)

00:22:51.453 --> 00:22:54.623
- Hey, Doc, what's going on?
- Stand by. I'll park over there.

00:22:55.332 --> 00:22:57.001
MARTY: Yeah, all right.

00:22:58.961 --> 00:23:00.838
Hey, right on time.

00:23:00.921 --> 00:23:02.506
Flying DeLorean.

00:23:02.590 --> 00:23:05.009
I haven't seen one of those in 30 years.

00:23:05.092 --> 00:23:06.093
(BOTH GRUNTING)

00:23:06.176 --> 00:23:07.344
Sorry. Excuse me. Sorry.

00:23:07.428 --> 00:23:08.888
(HORN HONKING)

00:23:08.971 --> 00:23:11.807
Hey, I'm walking here! I'm walking here!

00:23:12.725 --> 00:23:17.146
- What the hell?
- Don't drive, trank, low-res scuzzball!

