00:23:43.172 --> 00:23:45.424
Doc, Doc, Doc, look at this!

00:23:45.507 --> 00:23:47.176
It's changing.

00:23:53.015 --> 00:23:54.934
(INDISTINCT YELLING)

00:23:59.688 --> 00:24:01.941
