MARLENE: Mom? Mom, is that you?

00:28:33.545 --> 00:28:35.631
I gotta get out of here!

00:28:38.383 --> 00:28:40.135
(DOOR BELL RINGING)

00:28:40.219 --> 00:28:41.511
Mom!

00:28:50.312 --> 00:28:52.731
Mom? Mom, is that you?

