Marty, stay here. Just change clothes.
If I need you, I'll holler.

00:30:29.661 --> 00:30:31.330
Come on, Doc, I wanna check out my house.

00:30:31.413 --> 00:30:35.250
We can't risk you running
into your older self. Come on, Einie, let's go.

00:30:35.334 --> 00:30:37.753
Where's Jennifer? Where's Jennifer?

00:30:37.836 --> 00:30:39.421
Hilldale.

