00:33:52.280 --> 00:33:53.865
I'm having a hard time
keeping track of her these days.

00:33:53.949 --> 00:33:56.660
Hey, fruit. Fruit, please. Thank you.

00:33:56.743 --> 00:33:58.745
She's in one of those moods, I guess.
