00:34:25.522 --> 00:34:26.648
Hey, Needles.

00:34:26.731 --> 00:34:27.857
Needles?

00:34:27.941 --> 00:34:30.318
<i>So, did you take look
at that little business proposal of mine?</i>

00:34:30.402 --> 00:34:33.238
OLDER MARTY: I don't know, Needles.
NEEDLES: <i>What are you afraid of?</i>

00:34:33.321 --> 00:34:36.908
<i>If this thing works,
it'll solve all your financial problems.</i>

